                        <td>Summarize → Store</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>LangGraph</strong></td>
                        <td>Tool to build and run that logic</td>
                        <td>Kitchen automation system</td>
                        <td>LangGraph app</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <div class="workflow-box">
                <h4>🔄 Example Complete Workflow:</h4>
                <p><strong>User:</strong> "Hey Agent, summarize all case emails and update the DB."</p>
                <p><strong>Agent → LangGraph → Executes steps via MCP:</strong></p>
                <ol style="font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li>Fetch from PostgreSQL</li>
                    <li>Clean data</li>
                    <li>Summarize using Gemini</li>
                    <li>Embed using SentenceTransformer</li>
                    <li>Store in Qdrant</li>
                    <li>Return summary + similar cases</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>

